{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Get into the Christmas spirit with Magical Christmas\u00a0</strong>designed for the whole family. With cool graphics and a festive atmosphere, it will take you to a world full of color and joy. Enjoy a cheerful soundtrack with Christmas carols and Christmas melodies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Speed \u200b\u200band Precision Challenge:</strong></i> Players must think quickly and act accurately. Puzzle pieces fall from the top of the screen, and players must move them so that they fit in the right place before they reach the bottom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Competition and Cooperation:</i></strong>\u00a0For family and friends, there is a multiplayer mode, where players compete against each other to see who can complete the puzzle the fastest, or a cooperative mode where they work together to solve the puzzle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Progressive Levels:</strong></i> Different levels of pieces become more challenging and complex, requiring greater skill and concentration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Game Mode:</strong></i> Place the pieces as quickly as possible and you will be rewarded with combos. This helps you complete puzzles with 3 stars. If you fail, you will be penalized by having a piece already placed removed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Complete 10 puzzles in Junior mode.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3363420/beb69b503b76404a60837e9b1e98e9300cf4c054.jpg"},{"name":"Complete 10 puzzles in Senior mode.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3363420/beb69b503b76404a60837e9b1e98e9300cf4c054.jpg"},{"name":"Complete all puzzles in Junior mode.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/